speaker.name: Natan Mish
speaker.biography: Senior Machine Learning Engineer at Zimmer Biomet - the world's leading Orthopaedic medical devices company. London School of Economics graduate with an MSc in Applied Social Data Science. Passionate about using Machine Learning to solve complicated problems. I have experience analysing, researching and building data products in the financial, real estate, transportation and healthcare industries. Curious about (almost) everything and always happy to take on new experiences and challenges.
